    "summary": "Kubera exposes a portfolio data HTTP API plus MCP servers at `https://api.kubera.com/api/v1/mcp` and `https://api.kubera.com/api/v2/mcp`; the MCP surfaces use OAuth (v1) or an API/MCP token via `Authorization: Basic` (v2), while the HTTP API is documented publicly but its exact request auth mechanics could not be confirmed from the accessible docs.",
