        "setup": "Start the connection flow from an MCP client that supports OAuth, then approve Kubera on the authorization screen. Kubera's guide shows this for ChatGPT and Claude: open the client, add/connect the Kubera connector, then click **Connect > Authorize** as described in [MCP Setup Guide](https://help.kubera.com/article/167-kubera-mcp-config). After approval, the client receives and stores the OAuth access token."
